  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d5fc81ee5cab17fc18b3c72cf94dabc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: CultEvent
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Mechanomics.Core::EventData
  title: 'Client: Concerned Cultist'
  description: "Greetings office worker, my name is Brother Nazca Orion VI, of the
    Siblings of Steel. Our god, Robo T-Rex, was recently scrapped in the 50th annual
    Mecha-Dino Cup. While she\u2019s in the shop, we were hoping you could send over
    a new object of worship as a temporary stand-in. Anyone heavy and imposing would
    be great."
  suggestedSize: 1
  behaviour:
    rid: 3076055930109952079
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 3076055930109952079
      type: {class: SkillEvent, ns: , asm: Mechanomics.Core}
      data:
        requirements:
        - stat: 3
          amount: 3
        cashReward: 1500
        quotaReward: 1
        cashPenalty: 1500
        successText: We have an update to the raid on a Siblings of Steel facility
          in which high-ranking religious leader Nazca Orion was captured, police
          say that a MetaMech mech was recovered from the repurposed factory building.
          MetaMech claims no involvement with the religious organization.
        failureText: The Brothers of Steel have made another move after commandeering
          a MetaMech mech to flee a police raid. Local law enforcement is looking
          into the role MetaMech may have played in this case.
